node.text:
Make some noise for #RDC2019! Celebrating our community for building, exploring, and coming together through play. 
What’s RDC?
The Roblox Developers Conference (RDC) is an invite-only event where top Roblox developers and creators gather together to celebrate community achievements and learn about Roblox’s latest announcements. This event is designed to empower you and your fellow Roblox developers with the resources, best practices, and connections to help accelerate the success of your game.

node.text: Ten years ago, Twenty One Pilots brought down the house in Newport Music Hall. Now they’re here to rock the metaverse with an unforgettable show.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Roblox on September 17, 2021 tagging @twentyonepilots. May be an image of 2 people and text.

node.text:
It’s all been leading up to this.
You control the action in the @TwentyOnePilots Concert Experience, debuting today at 4 PM PT and repeating hourly until 9/19. Link in bio 👆
